headline: FIS Treasury & Risk Solutions Win Big at the 2025 Treasury Management International Awards for Innovation & Excellence
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., March 25, 2025--FIS® (NYSE: FIS), a global leader in financial technology, announced today that it has won two awards at the 2025 Innovation & Excellence awards from Treasury Management International. In the Technology & Innovation category, FIS won the Best Cash & Treasury Management Solution award for its Treasury and Risk Manager, Integrity Edition ("Integrity") solution.
